== Guides & Documentation

Key resources to support mentors, podlings, and the Incubator PMC. These guides cover onboarding, mentoring practices, governance, reporting, and lessons learned.

== Incubator Guides

These guides provide reference material for mentors, podlings, and IPMC members on every aspect of incubation — from getting started to graduation.  
They represent the written foundation for the Incubator’s training materials and slide decks.

=== Getting Started / Orientation
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Joining+the+Incubator[Joining the Incubator] — what to expect before applying, reasons to join (or not), and how the proposal process works  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Orientation+Guide[Podling Orientation Guide] — introduction to incubation and ASF culture  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Committer+Onboarding[Podling Committer Onboarding] — what new committers need to know  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+PPMC+Onboarding[Podling PPMC Onboarding] — duties and decision-making within the PPMC  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Onboarding[Mentor Onboarding] — step-by-step entry into mentoring  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+PMC+Onboarding[Incubator PMC Onboarding] — orientation for joining the IPMC  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Mentor+Quick+Start+Guide[Mentor Quick Start Guide] — fast orientation for new mentors  

